<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>FAQ | Music Festival</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/faq.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.2.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>
   

    <div class="faq-background">
        <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
        <div class="faq-container">
            <div class="faq">
                <h3 class="faq-title">What are the dates of the festival?</h3>
                <p class="faq-text">The festival will take place on June 20, 2024.</p>
                <button class="faq-toggle">
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                    <i class="fas fa-times"></i>
                </button>
            </div>
            <div class="faq">
                <h3 class="faq-title">Where is the festival located?</h3>
                <p class="faq-text">The festival is held at Central Park, Festival City, USA.</p>
                <button class="faq-toggle">
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                    <i class="fas fa-times"></i>
                </button>
            </div>
            <div class="faq">
                <h3 class="faq-title">What is the lineup for this year?</h3>
                <p class="faq-text">You can find the full lineup on our website under the Lineup section.</p>
                <button class="faq-toggle">
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                    <i class="fas fa-times"></i>
                </button>
            </div>
            <div class="faq">
                <h3 class="faq-title">Are there any age restrictions?</h3>
                <p class="faq-text">Yes, attendees must be 18 years or older to enter the festival.</p>
                <button class="faq-toggle">
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                    <i class="fas fa-times"></i>
                </button>
            </div>
            <div class="faq">
                <h3 class="faq-title">What items are prohibited at the festival?</h3>
                <p class="faq-text">Prohibited items include weapons, illegal substances, outside food and beverages, and professional camera equipment. Please refer to our website for the full list.</p>
                <button class="faq-toggle">
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                    <i class="fas fa-times"></i>
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="/js/faq.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
